Golang is an open source, compiled and statically typed programming language created by Google. 
Go is general purpose language hence can be used to develop mobile apps, desktop applications, 
web apps and many more. 
From my end, we used Golang to develop a web application.
If you have not considered using Go, you have to use Go for the following reasons
Built in Concurrency. https://vimeo.com/49718712  a talk from Rob Pike of the designers of go.
Fast Compilation 
Portable. You can port source code easily without worrying about dependencies.
